      "text": "The nose knows, and everyone knows, you don’t run from Border Patrol. 3/18 An Arizona man smuggling 4 illegal aliens drove away from agents but was stopped short by agents who deployed a spike strip for the vehicle. After a short foot chase, agents and K9 units tracked and arrested all subjects involved. All four aliens will be processed for removal proceedings under 8 USC 1182 and the driver will be prosecuted under for human smuggling charges under 8 USC 1324.\nThis incident remains under investigation and Tucson Sector will continue to collaborate with the U.S. Attorney’s Office to pursue all applicable criminal charges.",
